<L>__{exterior department store display window (chicago) }
<A>__{sidewalk night (short time later) pamela dresses a mannequin in the display window. as she moves behind the mannequin to fasten a garment she sees doug standing on the other side of the glass watching her from the sidewalk. doug writes a message on the plate glass window with his index finger (printing the letters in reverse so that the message is legible from pam's pov); his message reads: "i love you."}
